verbose_text: Experimental results showed that the protein expression of cytochrome C, caspase-9 and caspase-3 in the interference group significantly increased compared with the control group (P < 0.05) and more obviously in the drug combination group (the 5-FU + celecoxib group) (P < 0.05, Table XREF_TABLE).
evidence: expression of cytochrome C, caspase-9 and caspase-3
